  m_text: "Is hellfire worse than another week swiping on dating apps? \n\nThis torn
    up public library discard copy of the Necronomicon might be little more than
    a pile of loose paper. But with some ingenuity, I could summon up a hot demon
    to go out for coffee... or a hellhound that will drag me into eternal damnation.
    \n\nHonestly, getting pulled into the void sounds infinitely better than trying
    to turn another hundred \"Hey\" texts into a real conversation."
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
